  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      they also make you look super cool
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi84ZDE5MWQzNi01ZjcwLTQ0ZWItOGZhYS1iMmUxZTE5MTBlYmU_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--c4382b68b446ed4b55581fc18dbc5c1c51ab256d" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWs0WkRFNU1XUXpOaTAxWmpjd0xUUTBaV0l0T0daaFlTMWlNbVV4WlRFNU1UQmxZbVVHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--3296653c4cee7a0c44228e78a2296b471e29a6f3/IMG_3260.jpeg" filename="IMG_3260.jpeg" filesize="86043" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="especially in portrait mode"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_3260.jpeg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      especially in portrait mode
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>The colors -- rock and vegetation -- change a ton as you descend.&nbsp; Apparently you walk through <a href="https://www.dothecanyon.com/life-zones-its-founder-and-the-grand-canyon/">several life zones</a> on the way down.&nbsp; There's a lot of red, brown, and black, but also a ton of greenery.&nbsp; Also some lizards and an absurd number of ominously-cawing ravens.&nbsp; Advice about the hike stresses eating, drinking, and resting enough, and notes that "some may finish their Grand Canyon hike and swear to never backpack again -- however many folks, including older people and tiny babies, have made it in and out with no problem.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi82NzA2YWIzYy0zN2MxLTQ1YjMtYTZkZC05ZTM0Y2YzYTZhZTY_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--6786cc27004d8d03077501ae47c79b7ff6f05c46" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWsyTnpBMllXSXpZeTB6TjJNeExUUTFZak10WVRaa1pDMDVaVE0wWTJZellUWmhaVFlHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--7a2b76fbc08ea24bff1f1752e4ad4e13f906d3cf/IMG_3274.jpeg" filename="IMG_3274.jpeg" filesize="127685" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="one of the rest stops with a composting bathroom"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_3274.jpeg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      one of the rest stops with a composting bathroom
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi8zY2JhM2ZhNy03OTg1LTRkMDEtOTM2MS1lNGE3ZjIzMGE3N2Q_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--882a92089092cb4dda7f5ca486e628275589c4f6" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWt6WTJKaE0yWmhOeTAzT1RnMUxUUmtNREV0T1RNMk1TMWxOR0UzWmpJek1HRTNOMlFHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--885bd9c34c53cdbd07a023fc9684cb72ec002320/IMG_3262.jpeg" filename="IMG_3262.jpeg" filesize="155066" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="we put electrolyte tablets in our water to avoid dying of too much water (bottles from Elisa and Bob's beautiful &quot;three day festival of love&quot;)"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
