  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment>
</div><div><br></div><h1>Nearing The Bottom</h1><div>
<br>Eventually the Colorado River came into view.&nbsp; It seemed like we were very close, but really it was like another hour or so.&nbsp; There were a good number of folks on the trail, although many fewer after about the halfway point -- where it's recommended that day-trip hikers turn around and head back up.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9mN2MwNTZlMi0yM2U0LTQ1NGMtODUxYS1hZTc1YmMzYzE2OTM_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--e784d3ccebaaa00c818a40784679c49dc33df5b4" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxtTjJNd05UWmxNaTB5TTJVMExUUTFOR010T0RVeFlTMWhaVGMxWW1Nell6RTJPVE1HT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--9737e63bfefc759ab3b59cc31b9ecae805abb464/IMG_3286.jpeg" filename="IMG_3286.jpeg" filesize="134293" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="so close!"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_3286.jpeg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      so close!
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi82MzBjMGQyMi05Y2E0LTQyNDYtYWJhNi02NmJjZWExZjBhOGE_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--0147042750e9b604849795066d3766462b14a153" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWsyTXpCak1HUXlNaTA1WTJFMExUUXlORFl0WVdKaE5pMDJObUpqWldFeFpqQmhPR0VHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--30cb3943aecd8772a050eb8681e22903c8289043/IMG_3293.jpeg" filename="IMG_3293.jpeg" filesize="182763" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="lots and lots of switchbacks"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_3293.jpeg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      lots and lots of switchbacks
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>Near the end of the trail is the Black Bridge, which crosses the Colorado maybe half of a mile before the campsite.&nbsp; The hiking map warns not to swim in the Colorado because it's wide and swift, and I lost enough family members playing the Oregon Trail game to know not to take chances.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9jNmU2NWEzNi01NmU3LTQzODItOWE1Zi04MjE5NDM5MDE5M2I_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--1d3b51d1754e9e15fe4a04f2b4b764af2f9ecdb3" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxqTm1VMk5XRXpOaTAxTm1VM0xUUXpPREl0T1dFMVppMDRNakU1TkRNNU1ERTVNMklHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--55ca78666352f7c2f8a5257eea816a96a3d27534/IMG_3295.jpeg" filename="IMG_3295.jpeg" filesize="124917" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="a grand river for a grand canyon"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_3295.jpeg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      a grand river for a grand canyon
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>However you can raft and boat the river; we saw some folks putting in as we were finally crossing the Black Bridge.&nbsp; We set off from the trailhead at around 8:30am and arrive at 2:30pm; a pace a little above one mile per hour.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi84MWJmYWZjOC1lM2ZmLTQ4YjgtYmQ1MC1kOTViMGViYTVkNzg_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--6172bda8f5cd388802aac43f51a45b52ec1becbb" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWs0TVdKbVlXWmpPQzFsTTJabUxUUTRZamd0WW1RMU1DMWtPVFZpTUdWaVlUVmtOemdHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--fde6f70a0e4794323c9e60682204d713c8232bb7/IMG_3296.jpeg" filename="IMG_3296.jpeg" filesize="132973" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="lucky boaters"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_3296.jpeg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      lucky boaters
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>At the bottom are both the Bright Angel Campground, where we stayed, as well as <a href="https://www.grandcanyonlodges.com/lodging/phantom-ranch/">Phantom Ranch</a>, the only lodge at the bottom of the canyon.&nbsp; After arriving, we set up camp and wandered around a bit to check out the river and the ranch.&nbsp; We also saw a mom and baby mule deer crossing another small bridge over the Bright Angel creek on our way to the river.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi8wN2U5YTU1Ny0xZGZkLTQ2YzgtODM0OS1kOGU2ZTRjNDY1MzE_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--8e7cff2ec9578502e7f84998cef0aea10a24c531" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWt3TjJVNVlUVTFOeTB4Wkdaa0xUUTJZemd0T0RNME9TMWtPR1UyWlRSak5EWTFNekVHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--a670d35eb4ebb65d60d7d3eba31a0a5ae6bc49c8/IMG_3301.jpeg" filename="IMG_3301.jpeg" filesize="186758" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="The mom crosses the bridge, the baby decides to off-road and hopped down the small ledge to cross the hard way."><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpeg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_3301.jpeg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      The mom crosses the bridge, the baby decides to off-road and hopped down the small ledge to cross the hard way.
  </figcaption>
